  第二组：前台文章公开接口

- GET /api/articles
  - 作用：前台文章列表
  - 是否鉴权：否
  - 查询参数建议：
    - page
    - page_size
    - category_id
    - tag_id
    - keyword
  - 示例：
```
GET /api/articles?page=1&page_size=10&
category_id=2
```
- 返回数据建议：
```
{
  "list": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Go JWT 实战",
      "slug": "go-jwt",
      "cover": "/uploads/article/cover1.png",
      "status": "published",
      "views_count": 10,
      "likes_count": 3,
      "favorites_count": 1,
      "created_at": "2026-05-01T10:00:00Z",
      "author": { "id": 1, "username": "admin" },
      "category": { "id": 2, "name": "Go" },
      "tags": [{ "id": 1, "name": "JWT" }]
    }
  ],
  "total": 100,
  "page": 1,
  "page_size": 10
}
```
- 放置位置：
  
  - controller/article_controller.go ： GetArticleList
  - service/article_service.go ： GetArticleList
  - dao/article_dao.go ： ListArticles
- GET /api/articles/:id
  
  - 作用：前台文章详情
  - 是否鉴权：否
